body_html: We didn't have proper empty tensor support, so neither behavior you saw for 0.4.1 and the one you saw for 0.4.0 is desired. Now on master (and in next release) we have proper empty tensor support. So you will get a proper [3, 4, 2, 0] shaped tensor soon!
